  "texts": [
    "Various external factors, such as temperature, storage time, and other ambient factors affect the calendar lifetime of batteries.",
    "There are two main strategies to predict the calendar lifetime: experimental methods and computational simulations.",
    "Experimental methods provide direct evidence of battery degradation history, but it is time-consuming and expensive.",
    "Computational simulation can reduce the experimental cost, but depend on the availability of accurate models and comprehensive databases.",
    "The prediction for the life cycle of batteries usually covers different time scales, the state of charge (SOC) is within one cycle scale, while the lifetime prediction across the whole life period is referred to as the state of health (SOH) of the battery."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}